Key Personnel Added – Mark A. Smith, CEO (former CEO of Molycorp), Tony Fulton, former State Senator in Nebraska
State & Community Support – Overwhelming support from Elk Creek and Nebraskan population and politicians
Infrastructure – Excellent existing roads, power, water and rail on site
Only Niobium deposit in America

 
Location
The Elk Creek Carbonatite, located in southeastern Nebraska an hour south of Lincoln. The niobium deposit is roughly 800 x 400 x 400 meters. The deposit is open in 3 directions including at depth

 
