Niocorp Developments Ltd.


            
            NioCorp Developments Ltd. engages in the provision of exploration and development of mineral deposits. Its products include niobium, scandium, and titanium.  The company was founded on February 27, 1987 and is headquartered in Centennial, CO.

            
